Sundays was church. They were Baptists my - parents, and it was a case of in the younger days - being taken to church in the morning, having to go to Sunday school in the afternoon, and, when old enough, being taken to church again in the evenin
g. If not, left at home in charge of the maid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4413364 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9184678\charrsid6298070 Did you have different clothes on Sunday?
