Oh yes. Yes, we had - a - the newest rig out was - reserved for Sunday wear of course - I don't know whether this is of any interest, on one occasion when m
y parents were at church in the evening, when a burst water pipe upstairs flooded the bedroom and I was - you know, sort of sitting in bed getting thoroughly wet yelling at the top of my voice, and - I was - rescued by the maid and taken out and - then sh
e dashed off to church, because she didn't know how to - stop the water coming through, and fetched the parents home from church to - turn the water off, by which time the place was - beautifully flooded of course.
